posting_body: ['Prices subject to change.', "DISCOVER THE LUXURY IN HOUSTON'S INNER LOOP", "The Carlton offers a European escape in the heart of Houston's Inner Loop hub.", "The Carlton's Mediterranean stucco exterior, Palladian windows, arched colonnades, and private balconies and solariums envelop you with picturesque charm.", 'Walk to your favorite gourmet grocer, movie theater, shopping center or corner cafe.', "Experience world-class culture and delectable restaurants right outside your door, miles of biking trails at nearby Memorial Park, and Houston's vibrant downtown just minutes away.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 78', 'OR Text', '78', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1403 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Double Vanity Sinks*', '- WiFi Thermostat', '- Cultured Marble Countertops', '- Built-in Bookcases *', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Balconies or Solariums*', '- French Doors & Bay Windows *', '- Dramatic Vaulted Ceilings', '- Rain Showerhead', '- Wood-Styled Floors', '- Oversized Garden Tubs', '- Custom Crown Molding', '- Fireplaces*', '*select units', 'Community Amenities', '- Controlled Access/Gated', '- Meditation Garden', '- Latte Lounge', '- Rental Furniture Avail', '- Beautiful Pool', '- Dog Walk', '- Valet Trash Pick Up', '- Business Center', '- Fitness Center', 'Pet Policy', 'No breed or weight restrictions!', '2 pets maximum.', 'Call for full details!', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'The Carlton', '3805 West Alabama Street , Houston, TX, 77027', 'zkm9HDK8G']
